{"tiddlers":{"$:/plugins/oeyoews/neotw-error-better/readme":{"title":"$:/plugins/oeyoews/neotw-error-better/readme","description":"neotw-error-better","text":"> 愿每一个tiddlywiki用户都看不到红色报错弹窗警告

> 众所周知, tiddlywiki的弹窗报错就像windows的蓝屏警告一样, 几乎没有有效信息

<div class='tc-error-form relative'>

! JavaScript 内部错误

嗯，这很尴尬。建议您通过刷新浏览器来重新启动 TiddlyWiki

</div>
"},"$:/plugins/oeyoews/neotw-error-better/style.css":{"title":"$:/plugins/oeyoews/neotw-error-better/style.css","text":".tc-error-form {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff00adc9, #ff3b3b) !important;
	color: transparent !important;
	border: none !important;
	cursor: pointer;
  bottom: 8px;
  right: 8px;
	text-align: center;
  padding: 8px !important;
  height: 44px !important;
  width: 44px !important;
	border-radius: 50% !important;
	overflow: hidden;
	box-shadow: 0 0 2px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)
	transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.tc-error-form:hover {
	background: #00000018 !important;
	text-align: inherit;
  width: auto !important;
  height: auto !important;
	color: black !important;
  inset: 0px !important;
	border-radius: 4px !important;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  margin: 16px !important;
  padding: 16px;
	cursor: auto;
}","tags":"$:/tags/Stylesheet"}}}
